Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:30.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A beautiful heart, so strong and true
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:35.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A gentle to-ouch that I always tu-urn to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she helps me pu-ull through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These walls that I built up around
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:47.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Crumble do-own with that wondro-ous sound
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:51.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This timid voice that I've fo-ound
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:56.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her head upon my shoulde-er...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As she whispers in my ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The hurt we keep inside, it burns
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:09.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And when we never speak, we learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:14.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our silence has more power than we realize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:18.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But when we let it out, and cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And through tears we speak our minds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:27.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And find the words that ring true to our he-eart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:33.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every da-ay becomes better than the last
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her words, so soft, a pleasant plea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:56.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She voiced those thoughts that lived inside o-of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:59.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let my feelings flow free
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I face my pain by letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:08.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Put trust in fate and now I always ha-ave hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:12.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I no longer need to be alo-one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cuz her head's upon my shoulde-er...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:22.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As she whispers in my e-e-ear...
